article:
https://www.atlassian.com/blog/git/alternatives-to-git-submodule-git-subtree

to add:
git subtree add --prefix src/spotify-sdk https://github.com/loverajoel/spotify-sdk.git master --squash

to update:
git subtree pull --prefix src/spotify-sdk https://github.com/loverajoel/spotify-sdk.git master --squash

to contribute back:
git remote add spotify-sdk-upstream git@github.com:heavyk/spotify-sdk.git
git subtree push --prefix src/spotify-sdk spotify-sdk-upstream master
